83220/extras/58c75ad177efb59187608afa7230a891.avif?t=1760761373\" width=800 height=422 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Connect the scenes in your dreams and take your abilities to different worlds. However, at times, opening a bridge often means one-way closure of certain portals. Therefore, make good use of your abilities, plan your route, and complete one puzzle after another</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983220/extras/db131262a41055c9e74eb4571d500dfc.poster.avif?t=1760761373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983220/extras/db131262a41055c9e74eb4571d500dfc.webm?t=1760761373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983220/extras/db131262a41055c9e74eb4571d500dfc.mp4?t=1760761373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
